item.description: Chao Huang is now a research assistant in the Chinese University of Hong Kong, advised by Prof. Chi-Wing Fu. He got the B.Eng. from ESE Department, Nanjing University in 2019, working with Prof. Zhan Ma. Actively looking for Phd position.
